The Google Maps Scraper is an Apify tool that extracts data from Google Maps without requiring an API key or Google account. It functions as an alternative to the official Google Places API.

## Key Capabilities

The scraper collects comprehensive business listing information including:

- Images and location data

```json
  "searchStrings": ["plumbers", "electricians", "HVAC contractors"],
  "locations": ["Chicago, IL"],
  "includeWebsites": true,
  "includePhones": true,
  "includeEmails": true,
  "maxPlaces": 1000
}
```

```bash
curl -X POST https://api.apify.com/v2/acts/compass/crawler-google-places/runs \
```
